TECHNICAL REQUIREMENTS DOCUMENT (TRD)
1. Architecture Decision
Framework: Zero-framework — pure static HTML/CSS/JS
No build step: No npm, no webpack, no TypeScript, no React
Deployment: Vercel static hosting, GitHub-connected (auto-deploy on main push)
CMS: Custom localStorage admin with GitHub API as publish layer

Rationale: Maximum simplicity, zero dependency maintenance, instant Vercel deploys, full design control without framework constraints.

