5. scripts.js Requirements
Single shared JS file loaded via <script src="scripts.js"></script> in every page footer.

Functions:

Font FOUT guard: document.fonts.ready.then(() => document.body.classList.add('fonts-ready'))
Mobile menu: Toggle .open on .nav-links and .active on .menu-toggle on click
Dropdown toggle (≤900px): Toggle open class on parent li for .dropdown-toggle buttons
Case study accordion: One-at-a-time expand/collapse using max-height: scrollHeight
Scroll reveal: IntersectionObserver on all .reveal elements → add .visible
Blog filter: .filter-btn click → filter .blog-card by data-category, toggle .active on button
Parallax: Passive scroll listener → translateY(scrollY * (i+1) * 0.03) per .parallax-shape
Modal open/close: [data-modal] triggers open; overlay click and .modal-close trigger close
Active nav: Compare window.location.pathname.split('/').pop() to link href → add .active
