13. Security Notes
admin.html not publicly linked from the main nav (direct URL access only)
GitHub PAT: Stored in localStorage (plain text) — acceptable for single-user personal site
No server-side secrets: All credentials client-side by design
Content HTML: Generated with escHtml() function to prevent XSS in metadata fields
